Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.00,0:00:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\b1}The Faceless Ones: Episode 4{\b\b}\N{\b1\b1}无面一族: 第四集{\b\b}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.00,0:00:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,【中文翻译/时间轴】巴蛮子sz
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.56,0:00:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,- 都搞定了  - 很好\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- All set.   - Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.67,0:00:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是想知道变色龙观光游的秘密吗?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}You wanted to know the secret of Chameleon Tours.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.84,0:01:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,好了, 督察...\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Well Inspector,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.52,0:01:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你自己看!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}see for yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.32,0:01:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,- 博士!   - 他死了!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Doctor!   - He's dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.56,0:01:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你跟我来\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}You're coming with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.50,0:01:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会离开他\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I'll not leave him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.92,0:01:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你有五秒钟改变主意\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}You have five seconds to change your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.02,0:01:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,除非你先杀了我\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}You'll have to kill me then.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.46,0:01:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我说了五秒\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I said five seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.73,0:01:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,五, 四, 三...\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Five, four, three...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.44,0:01:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,SAMANTHA​!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}SAMANTHA!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.35,0:02:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我想问这飞机往哪儿开, 估计问也白问\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I suppose there's no use my asking\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}where this plane's going to?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.89,0:02:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你很快就能知道了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}You will know soon enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.71,0:02:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,三号飞机呼叫基地\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}This is Plane Number Three to Base.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.23,0:02:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉总管我已经按他吩咐给他找了一个替身\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Inform the Director that I have\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}an original for him as ordered.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.01,0:02:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,正在运送过来\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I am delivering him now,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.09,0:02:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,然后会立刻返回盖特威克机场\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}and will return immediately to Gatwick Airport.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.82,0:03:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Jamie? 你没事吧\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Jamie? Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.40,0:03:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,没事. 他们..没有伤到你吧, 有吗?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Aye. Th... They've not harmed you, have they?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.79,0:03:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,没有, 但我动不了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}No - but I can't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.44,0:03:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,博士?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.54,0:03:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你没事吧?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.95,0:03:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,发生什么了? 我...我动不了了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}What's happening? I... I can't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.10,0:03:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什么?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.19,0:03:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我...我不知道, 是一束光\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I... I don't know. It's a beam of light.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.16,0:03:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,是. 博士, 它...在朝我们移动!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Aye. Doctor, it... it's moving towards us!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.88,0:03:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,这对于将要发生在我们身上的事来说, 只是一道小小的开胃菜\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}That's just a small fore-taste\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}of what'll happen to us
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.72,0:03:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,要是我们还不赶紧挪开的话\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}if we don't move and quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.72,0:03:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,- 但我动不了, 博士!   - 我也动不了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- But I can't move, Doctor!  - Neither can I.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.57,0:03:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下, 我可以移动一只胳膊\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Wait a minute. I can move one arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.54,0:03:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,但我移动不了!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}But I can't move away!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.29,0:04:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,噢博士! 你不能想什么办法停掉它吗?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Oh Doctor! Can't you do anything to stop it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.64,0:04:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,没有\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.96,0:04:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,等等, 有一个\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Wait. One thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.75,0:04:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然机会不大, 但也许能成功\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}It's a long chance but it just might work.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.04,0:04:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你包里有镜子吗?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Have you got a mirror in that bag?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.40,0:04:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,- 有  - 我看看\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Yes.   - Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.42,0:04:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯, 这应该可以. 把它给我\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Yes, that'll do. Hand it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.21,0:04:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,- 给不了  - 我没法移动我的手\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- I can't.  - I can't move my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.24,0:04:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Jamie, 你能拿到吗?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Jamie, can you take it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.65,0:04:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你拿到了吗?   - 还没, 小心!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Have you got it?   - No, careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.94,0:04:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,- 接着!  - 接到了!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Take it!   - Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.89,0:04:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,现在, 看看你能否把它对准那个射线枪\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Right now, see if you can point it at that laser gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.30,0:04:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,- 墙上的那个东西 - 我试试, 博士. 不过为啥?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- That thing on the wall.\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- I'll try, Doctor. But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.61,0:04:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你能把光反射回去, 我们就有机会了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}If you can reflect the light back,\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}we've got a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.76,0:04:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你不能拿什么东西撑住它吗\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Can't you prop it up on something?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.34,0:04:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,不, 不行.\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}No, it won't work..
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.44,0:04:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我, 我用手拿着吧  - 但是你...你的手!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}-I'll... I'll have to hold it. - But your...your hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.67,0:04:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,这个风险我不得不担\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}It's a risk I'll have to take.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.45,0:04:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,快 Jamie! 赶紧!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Quick Jamie! Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.30,0:05:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,噢, 干得好!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Oh, well done!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.47,0:05:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,啊...我可以动了!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Argh... I can move!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.00,0:05:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我...我觉得是否...\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I... I wonder if...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.55,0:05:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得 Ben 和 Polly 是不是也遭遇了这个, 博士?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Do you think that's what happened\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}to Ben and Polly, Doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.68,0:05:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不是  - 你肯定吗?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- No.   - Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.76,0:05:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得他们拿他俩有别的用途\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I think they were needed for some purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.28,0:05:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,- 而我们没有?   - 显然我们对他们太危险了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- And we weren't.\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- We were obviously too dangerous for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.88,0:05:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,竟然想干这样的事情, 在光天化日之下!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}But to try and do something like this,\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}in broad daylight!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.32,0:05:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊. 这只可能意味着一件事情, 恐怕\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Yes. That means only one thing, I'm afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.93,0:05:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,他们的计划快要完成了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Their plans are almost complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.24,0:05:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我们必须赶紧行动, 否则别想就 Polly 和 Ben 了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}We'll have to act fast\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}if we're going to save Ben and Polly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.75,0:05:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,还有 Brian, 你是不是已经忘记他了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}And Brian, or have you forgotten about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.32,0:05:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,没, 我没有忘记他, Sam\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}No, I've not forgotten him Sam,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.13,0:05:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,但如果我的猜测没错的话, 他们都在同一个地方\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}but if my guess is right,\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}they're all in the same place.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.36,0:05:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,- 在什么地方?   - 我不知道\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- And where's that?  - I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.24,0:05:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,等等! 急救站!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Wait! The first aid post!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.81,0:05:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在那个监视器里面看到了一个急救站\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}We saw a first aid post on that monitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.92,0:05:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我们必须找到它\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}We must find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.85,0:05:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,快点, 你没打算在这里坐一整天吧, 有吗?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Come on, you're not going to\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}sit there all day are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.39,0:05:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下, 我们不能全都涌去急救站\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Just a minute. We can't all\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}go down to the Medical Unit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.56,0:05:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧, 我能干点什么?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}All right. What can I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.68,0:05:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,那个想杀我们的男人, 你有没有看清楚?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Did you get a good look\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}at the man who tried to kill us?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.64,0:06:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,应该有吧, 我都用脖子勒住他脖子了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I'll say. I had my arms around his neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.00,0:06:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,去变色龙的柜台, 看看能否看到他进出\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Go down to the Chameleon Kiosk\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}and see if he comes in or out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.82,0:06:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,但是小心点, 别让他看见你\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}But be careful. Don't let him see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.43,0:06:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我小心点? 你俩自己小心点吧, 我肯定没事\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Me be careful!? You two watch out\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}for yourselves! I'll be OK!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.17,0:06:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,她很有勇气, 那个小姑娘, 博士\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}She's got a lot of courage,\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}that wee lass, Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.99,0:06:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,是, 我只是期望她不要太冒险了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Yes. I just hope she doesn't\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}try to be too adventurous.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.27,0:06:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你是谁?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.84,0:06:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Steven Christopher​ Jenkins\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Steven Christopher Jenkins
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.08,0:06:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你住在哪里?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Where do you live?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.57,0:06:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我父母一起住在温布尔顿\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}With my parents in Wimbledon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.90,0:06:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,职业呢?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Employment?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.45,0:06:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我是个移民局官员, 在盖特威克机场工作\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I'm an Immigration Officer, at Gatwick Airport.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.32,0:06:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,过来, 慢点. 你很快就没事了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Come along, easy. You'll be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.98,0:06:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,过来, 慢点\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Now come along, take it easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.63,0:06:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我们马上会让你安然无恙\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}We'll have you as right as rain in a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.48,0:06:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,现在在这里坐下FIXME, 就这里\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Now just get you down here. There we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.34,0:06:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,- 很好  - 我怎么样, 博士?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Splendid.   - How am I doing, Doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.39,0:06:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,很好, 但不要装过头了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Very well but don't over do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.74,0:06:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,是了, 就是这个房间. 我们在监视器上看到的\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Yes, this is the room we saw on the TV monitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.34,0:06:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,如果这些药片没作用, 再过来找我\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}If the tablets do not help, come and see me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.45,0:07:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他这是怎么了?   - 是一种罕见的热带疾病\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- What's the matter with him?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- It's a rare tropical disease,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.95,0:07:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,护士, 我是他的医生\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Nurse. I'm his doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.20,0:07:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他不能很快恢复, 我们就...\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}If he doesn't rally soon we shall err...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.30,0:07:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我们就得给他用点梭玛林\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}we shall have to use somnalin.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.26,0:07:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,- 梭玛林?   - 是的...对, 梭玛林\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Somnalin?  - Yes... yes, somnalin
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.88,0:07:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我得找个地方让他躺下\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}So l have to get him somewhere to lie down.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.92,0:07:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,哦对了, 这里应该很合适\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Oh yes, this will do nicely.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.22,0:07:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,恐怕..你不能进里面去\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I... I'm afraid you can't go there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.12,0:07:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么不能? 这只是个X光室, 是吧?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Why not? It's just an X-ray room, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.42,0:07:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,屏风后面不是张躺椅吗?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Isn't that a couch behind the screen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.68,0:07:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉, 医生, 你不能把你的病人带进去\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I'm sorry, Doctor.\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}You can't take your patient in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.55,0:07:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你拒绝给我的病患帮助?   - 不, 不是这样的\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- You refuse to help my patient?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Oh, it's not that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.73,0:07:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我有一个病人要来拍X光片  - 哦, 我明白了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- I have someone coming for an X-ray.  - Oh I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.38,0:07:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,那你怎么不一开始就告诉我呢?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Well why didn't you tell me in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.32,0:07:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,来把你扶出去\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&\i1}Let's get you out of here.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.87,0:07:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,这个博士对我们的计划是个威胁\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}That Doctor is a menace to our plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.17,0:07:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,那我们必须杀了他\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Then we must kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.66,0:07:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我试过了, 他肯定是又逃掉了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I tried. He must have escaped.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.80,0:07:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他们从我这里逃不了  - 不, 等等\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- They won't escape me.  - No, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.29,0:07:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,这一次, 让他们来找我们\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}This time, let them to come to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.37,0:08:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直在联系他, 警司, 但他一直没接\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I've been paging him, Superintendent,\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}but he hasn't responded.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.06,0:08:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,是, 很好, 先生. 我会继续尝试\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Yes, very well sir. I'll keep on trying.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.51,0:08:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,接线员. 我订了一个到雅典的电话, 现在怎样了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Operator. Look, I booked a call through\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}to Athens, now what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.76,0:08:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,对, 好吧. 我在电话旁边等着\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Yes, very well, I'll stay near the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.71,0:08:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,这都是怎么回事?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}What's all this about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.49,0:08:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,- 噢博士, 你见到 Crossland 督察了吗?   - 没有, 怎么了?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Oh Doctor, have you seen Inspector Crossland?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Well no. Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.12,0:08:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,哦, 苏格兰场在找他, 但我们在哪里都找不到\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Well, Scotland Yard are looking for him\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}and we can't find him anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.43,0:08:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,还有, Briggs 小姐想找你\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Also, your Miss Briggs wants to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.14,0:08:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,但我跟她说了...她现在在哪儿?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}But I told her to... Where is she now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.92,0:08:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,她说要去什么变色龙柜台\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Well she said something about\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}going to the Chameleon Kiosk.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.23,0:08:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你去她那里看看, Jamie\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Go down and join her, Jamie.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.23,0:08:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,她这个年轻女人很有主见\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}She's a very strong headed young woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.70,0:08:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,- 确保她不会碰到什么麻烦  - 我会看着她的, 博士\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- See she doesn't come to any trouble.\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- I'll keep an eye on her, Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.84,0:08:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,总指挥, 督察说过他要去哪儿了吗?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Commandant, did the Inspector say\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}where he was going?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.41,0:08:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,唔, 他说他要去找变色龙观光游问问情况\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Hmm, oh he said he was going to\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}make some enquires about Chameleon Tours.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.83,0:08:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,但他现在不见了?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}And now he's disappeared?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.81,0:08:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你这结论下得也太快了吧?   - 我没觉得\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Aren't you rather jumping to conclusions?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.16,0:09:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我的两个朋友牵涉进变色龙观光游, 他俩都不见了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}My two friends became involved with Chameleon\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Tours, and they've both disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.24,0:09:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道我的猜测是什么\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}However, you know what I think has happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.05,0:09:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,是的, 你也知道我对你那荒谬的想法是怎么看的\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Yes, and you know what I think\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}about your ridiculous theory.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.49,0:09:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,外太空来的人, 真的是\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}People from outer space, indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.69,0:09:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你这是怎么了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Something the matter with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.29,0:09:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,总指挥, 我发现是怎么回事了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Commandant, I've found out what's been happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.63,0:09:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,好, 朝着正确的方向迈近了一步\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Well, that's a step in the right direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.49,0:09:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我的意思是, 我擅做主张, 给所有机场打了电话\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Wh... what I mean is, I took the liberty\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}of phoning all the airports
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.21,0:09:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,所以变色龙飞去的地方\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}that ah... Chameleon Tours fly to.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.23,0:09:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,最后打的是雅典\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}The last on my list was Athens.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.83,0:09:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你就没意识到到雅典的电话费...\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Don't you realise the expense of phoning Ath...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.34,0:09:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,是的我知道, 我很抱歉\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Yes, I know, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.21,0:09:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我发现的是, 他们从来没有成功运送任何乘客\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}But what I found out is -\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}they never deliver any passengers.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.85,0:09:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你说的什么意思? 从来没有成功运送任何乘客?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}What do you mean? Never deliver any passengers...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.32,0:09:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,绝对是真的, 先生. 他们说的全都一样\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}It's absolutely true, sir.\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}They all say the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.97,0:09:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,杜布罗夫尼克, 雅典, 罗马\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Dubrovnik, Athens, Rome.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.48,0:09:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,他们说年轻乘客搭上飞机去其它地方, 但是...\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}They say they pick up young passengers\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}to take them off to other places but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.84,0:09:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,没有一个人到达任何地方!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}none of them ever arrive anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.73,0:09:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,要是这样的话, 他们肯定把这些人运到了某个秘密的机场\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Well in that case, they must be flying\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}these young people to some secret airfield.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.93,0:09:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,- 但是为什么呢?  - 你仍然还是地球人的思维\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- But why?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- You're still thinking in Earth terms.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.92,0:09:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我还就打算坚持这样\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}And I intend to go on doing so.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.22,0:09:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,- 那个变色龙的飞行员叫什么名字?   - Blade 机长\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- What was the name of that Chameleon Pilot?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Captain Blade.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.94,0:09:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,- 飞机预计什么时候回来  - 还有半个小时, 先生\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- And what time is the plane due back?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- About half an hour, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.66,0:10:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,好, 等这次掉头了, 这次我们派人跟着\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Right. After the turn-round\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}we'll have it followed this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.81,0:10:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我能跟你说句话吗, 亲爱的?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Could I have a word with you, my dear?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.22,0:10:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,给我接皇家空军曼斯顿站\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Get me the RAF Station Manston.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.37,0:10:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我怀疑急救中心跟这一切有联系\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I suspect that the Medical Centre\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}is connected with all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.18,0:10:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,- 急救中心..得了  - 请不要跟他一样\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Medical Cen... Oh come on...\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Now please don't get like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.30,0:10:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,是的, 这里绝对有联系\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Oh yes, there is definitely a connection.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.20,0:10:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,现在, 我打算进里面去, 看一圈\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Now, I would like to get in there\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}and have a look round.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.76,0:10:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,任何人都可以进去啊\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}But anyone can go in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.24,0:10:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,但我期望能先把那个护士引开\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}But I would like to get that nurse\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}out of the way first...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.66,0:10:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得你能帮我搞定吗?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Do you think that you can manage it for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.13,0:10:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你看吧, 给你办得妥妥的\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}You'll find that in order.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.15,0:10:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,他说你会做些傻事\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}He said you'd do something silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.65,0:10:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗? 他还说什么了?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Oh yeah, what else did he say?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.56,0:10:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他说你很有主见  - 很好, 你可以告诉博士\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- He said you were headstrong.\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Oh great. Look, you can tell the Doctor
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.65,0:10:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,他不可能说服我放弃这个, 你也不能\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}he's not going to talk me out of this one,\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}and neither are you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.15,0:10:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我要登上变色龙的下一次航班, 还有半小时起飞\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I'm going on the next Chameleon flight,\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}that leaves in half an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.96,0:10:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你还没有明白吗, 这是我们能查出点什么的唯一途径\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Oh look don't you see, it's the only way\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}we can find out anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.65,0:10:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,哦, 别担心, 我会回来告诉把全部经过都告诉你的\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Oh, don't worry. I'll come back\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}and tell you all about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.90,0:10:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,- 那得是能回来  - 哦, 只是去一趟罗马罢了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- If you do come back.\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Oh, it's only going to Rome.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.26,0:11:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,凭什么你确信你能在罗马找到你弟弟?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}And what makes you so sure\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}you'll find your brother in Rome?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.48,0:11:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,哦, 我不知道. 但那是他本来应该抵达的地方\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Oh, I don't know. But that's where\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}he was supposed to be going.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.41,0:11:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,至少我可以做点什么\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}At least I'll be doing something.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.11,0:11:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,是. 但你没有意识到这有多危险\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Aye, but do you not realise how dangerous it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.52,0:11:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你可能是害怕了, 我可没有\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Look if you're scared, I'm certainly not.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.13,0:11:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,- 要是博士在这里就好了  - 噢\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- I wish the Doctor were here.  - Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.21,0:11:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿, 也许我可以和你一起去\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Hey, maybe I could go with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.68,0:11:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿, 这还差不多.\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Hey, now you're talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.78,0:11:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得你买得机票吗?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Do you think you can you raise the lolly?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.35,0:11:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,- 机票?   - 费用, 钱\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- The lolly?  - The brass, the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.91,0:11:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,会花费你28块钱, 或者说英镑\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Look it will cost you twenty-eight\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}quid - pounds to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.14,0:11:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,哦, 那是好大一笔钱. 我从来没有这么多钱\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Oh but that's a fortune.\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I've never seen that much money in my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.51,0:11:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我估计..我不能可以替你去吗?  - 不行\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- I suppose I couldn't take your place? - No!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.29,0:11:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,博士说这可不是一个小姑娘能干的事情\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}The Doctor said it was er...\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}no job for a wee lassie...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.47,0:11:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,- 一个小姑娘! 你可以告诉博士... - 说再见吧\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- A wee lassie! You can tell the Doctor...\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- I say goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.55,0:11:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿, 小子!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Hey, kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.56,0:11:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以照顾好自己, 知道吧\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I can take care of myself, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.79,0:11:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是不太放心\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I just wanted to make sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.58,0:11:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,唔, 所以你可以安排人跟踪?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Hmm. So you can arrange to have it followed?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.22,0:11:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,好, 我会搞明白的\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Good. Oh I'll find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.48,0:12:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,变色龙的下一趟航班什么时候?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}What time's the next Chameleon flight?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.22,0:12:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,15:30飞罗马, 先生\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}1530hrs to Rome, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.76,0:12:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,15:30 往南飞\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}1530hrs heading South.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.27,0:12:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,好, 等他们请求起飞的时候我会通知你\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Right. And I'll let you know\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}when they request permission to start up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.16,0:12:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,再见老伙计, 很是感谢\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Cheerio old man and many thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.97,0:12:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,好了, 都安排妥了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Well, that's settled that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.86,0:12:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,变色龙的下一趟航班就会有皇家空军跟在它后面了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}The next Chameleon flight\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}will have an RAF fighter on its tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.61,0:12:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,老天, Jean, Jean!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Good grief. Jean. Jean!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.56,0:12:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,这姑娘怎么了? 找急救中心\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}What's the matter with the girl?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Get me the Medical Centre.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.25,0:12:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你的助手不能自己到这里来吗, 总指挥?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Isn't it possible for your assistant\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}to come down here, Commandant.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.96,0:12:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,但我不能离开这里啊\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}But I'm not supposed to leave here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.96,0:12:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧, 先生, 既然你坚持的话\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}All right sir, if you insist.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.29,0:13:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我要下班了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I'm just going off duty,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.96,0:13:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,但这位先生会很高兴继续照顾你\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}but err this gentleman\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}will be pleased to attend to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.18,0:13:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你现在觉得怎样  - 不太好\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- How do you feel now?  - Not too good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.63,0:13:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我就不明白了, 她从来没有这样过\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I can't understand it.\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}She's never done this on me before.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.21,0:13:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你护士, 我现在觉得好多了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Thank you Nurse. I feel much better now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.36,0:14:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,那就应该没有什么大事\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Well there couldn't be much wrong then.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.29,0:14:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你吃过午饭了吗?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Have you had any lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.60,0:14:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,没, 我今天一直很忙, 连早饭都还没有吃\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}No I've been so busy today,\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I haven't even had any breakfast.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.39,0:14:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,那怪不得你会不舒服了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Then no wonder you didn't feel well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.84,0:14:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,真的总指挥, 你必须得让你的下属有时间按时吃饭\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Really Commandant. You must see that\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}your staff have time for regular meals.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.27,0:14:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我从没阻止过她吃午饭!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I've never stopped her having her lunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.88,0:14:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我确信, 总指挥, 但这种事总还是会发生\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I'm sure, Commandant.\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}But it has been known to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.00,0:14:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,- 来看看这儿  - 做得很好!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Now look here.   - Very well done!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.08,0:14:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我有没有给你足够时间  - 很多时间\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Did I give you enough time? - Ample time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.04,0:14:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,这都是怎么回事? 你完全就没病, 对不?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}What is all this?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}You weren't ill at all, were you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.69,0:14:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,没事了, 总指挥, 她是按我的指示在演戏\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}It's all right, Commandant.\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}She was acting on my instructions.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.48,0:14:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,- 按你的指示?  - 是. 你对这些东西怎么看\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- On your instructions?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Yes. What do you think of these?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.60,0:14:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,这些是什么?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Now, what are these?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.16,0:14:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我猜这里有人能告诉我们\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I think there's somebody here who can tell us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.90,0:14:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,打扰了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.35,0:14:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,一直坐在这里的那个家伙哪里去了?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Where's the chap who usually sits there?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.12,0:14:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,哦他很可能是下班了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Well he's probably off duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.61,0:14:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,如果是这样的话, 他应该过几个小时就会回来上班了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}In that case, he'll be back on shift\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}in a couple of hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.41,0:14:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了. 好吧, 看来得等了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I see. Oh well, these'll have to wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.83,0:15:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,变色龙青年观光游通知您\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Chameleon Youth Tours announce the departure
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.41,0:15:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,飞往罗马的419航班即将起飞\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}of their flight number Four-One-Nine to Rome.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.48,0:15:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,请所有旅客在候机室集合\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Will all passengers please\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}assemble in the departure lounge.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.39,0:15:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,不要忘了您的明信片\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Don't forget your postcards.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.24,0:15:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,把它们交给我, 我们将会帮你们寄出去...\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Give them back to me\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}and we'll post them for you when...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.61,0:15:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你找到你的机票了吗?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Have you found your ticket yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.50,0:15:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道, 好像是在某个地方弄丢了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I don't know. I seem to have lost it somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.69,0:15:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,但你认得我的, 对吧, 我从你这里买的票\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}But you remember me, don't you?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I bought the ticket off you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.79,0:15:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,又太多人了...名字是什么?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}There are so many people...\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}what was the name?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.01,0:15:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,呃, Samantha Briggs\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Err, Samantha Briggs.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.58,0:15:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,噢, 机票上写的是 S. Briggs\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Oh, it had S. Briggs on the ticket.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.72,0:15:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}S. Briggs has already checked in.\NS. Briggs 已经检票进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.77,0:15:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,哦不. 到底是谁...\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Oh no. Well, who the heck...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.24,0:15:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你记得那姑娘长什么样吗?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Look, can you remember what she looked like?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.77,0:15:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,姑娘? 我好像记得拿票的是个小伙子\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}She? I seem to remember a boy with that ticket.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.81,0:15:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Jamie! 他偷走了票. 我说, 你们必须要拦住他!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Jamie! He's pinched it.\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Look you have to stop him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.85,0:15:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我没法拦住飞机\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I can't hold up the flight.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.61,0:15:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,- 但是听着...   - 我很抱歉\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- But look...  - I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.74,0:15:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我帮不了你什么了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}There's nothing more\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I can do for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.05,0:15:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你好\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.58,0:15:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,是的, 好, 你真是太好了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Yes, all right. That's very kind of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.44,0:15:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你很幸运, 你的票找到了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}You're very fortunate.\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Your ticket's just been found.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.33,0:15:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,- 噢好, 谁捡到了?  - 恐怕我们不能告诉你\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Oh good. Well who got it?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- We can't tell you that I'm afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.93,0:16:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,但我们经理想要见你, 那就在那边\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}But our manager would like to see you.\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}He's just through there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.69,0:16:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,好, 拜\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Oh right, ta.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.77,0:16:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,现在, 谁的明信片准备好了?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Now, who's got their postcards ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.89,0:16:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,- 呃, 是你想见我?  - 是, 的确\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Er, you wanted to see me?  - Yes, indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.96,0:16:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你再也逃不了了!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}You won't escape again!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.20,0:16:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,变色龙419, 准许出港\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Chameleon Four-One-Nine. Clearance correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.61,0:16:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,变色龙419, 准许滑行\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Chameleon Four-One-Nine. Taxi Clearance?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.31,0:16:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,变色龙419, 沿南滑行道滑行,\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Chameleon Four-One-Nine.\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Taxi following southern taxiway
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.95,0:16:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,- 准备离开27号跑道  - 收到\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- for departure runway two-seven. - Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.63,0:16:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,这一次他们就有皇家空军跟在屁股后面了!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Well this time they'll have the RAF on their tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.43,0:16:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,如今这些战斗机可以到达多高, 总指挥?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}How high can fighters go these days, Commandant?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.50,0:16:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,- 哦, 十英里以上  - 好逊\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Oh, ten miles plus. - How futile.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.23,0:16:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,- 曼斯顿皇家空军基地, 先生  - 哦好\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- RAF Manston, sir.  - Oh, good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.65,0:16:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你好, 老小子. 变色龙的罗马航班刚刚起飞\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Hello, old boy.\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}The Chameleon Rome flight's just taken off.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.07,0:17:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,他们在琥珀一号上, 飞行高度210\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}They're on Amber One,\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}at flight level two-one-zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.52,0:17:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,好, 祝好\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Right. Good man.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.08,0:17:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你们可以解开安全带了, 谢谢\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}You can unfasten your seat belts now. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.57,0:17:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你没事吧?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.85,0:17:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,- 啊, 我会没事的  - 好\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Oh aye, I'll be all right. - Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.44,0:17:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,他们正要跨越50英里的标记点\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}That's the fifty-mile mark they're passing now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.34,0:17:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,通常你们在这个距离看不到他们吧\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Normally you don't plot them at this range?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.55,0:17:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,看不到, 有太多飞机需要控制了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}No, there's too much traffic to control.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.10,0:17:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,一旦他们起飞, 进入空中走廊, 就跟我们没关系了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Once they're up and away on their air corridor,\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}we're finished with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.32,0:17:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你好, 盖特威克机场\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Hello, Gatwick Airport.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.36,0:17:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,这里是皇家空军241号, 你们可以听到吗?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}This is RAF Two-Four-One. How do you read me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.08,0:17:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,盖特威克机场答复RAF-241, 我们可以清晰地听到\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Gatwick Airport to RAF Two-Four-One.\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}We read you loud and clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.75,0:17:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,变色龙的飞机正在视野内\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Have the Chameleon aircraft in sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.65,0:17:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,正在一万英尺高度尾随, 朝南飞行\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Am following at ten thousand feet, heading due south.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.92,0:17:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,就是他, 咬住尾巴. 目前看来进展不错!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}That's him. Right on the tail. So far so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.88,0:17:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,都搞定了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}All set.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.58,0:18:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,有什么东西在跟着我们\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Something's following us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.40,0:18:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,有另外一家飞机走同一路线?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Another airliner going the same way?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.76,0:18:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,不, 太小了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}No, it's too small.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.86,0:18:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,是架战斗机. 给我雷达数据\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}It's a fighter. Give me a radar reading.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.34,0:18:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,方位23-79\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Two-three decimal seven-nine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.56,0:18:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Heslington, 战斗机偏离航线了!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Heslington, that fighter's off course!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.13,0:18:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,盖特威克机场呼叫RAF-241, 你可以听到吗?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Gatwick to RAF Two-Four-One. Do you read me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.61,0:18:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,那飞机可不是简单地偏离航线\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}That plane isn't just off course.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.50,0:18:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,- 有事情发生了  - 你说得对, 它失控了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Something's happened to it.\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- You're right. It's out of control.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.84,0:18:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,盖特威克机场呼叫RAF-241, 你可以听到吗?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Gatwick to RAF Two-Four-One. Do you read me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.47,0:18:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得你收不到回答了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I don't think you'll get a reply.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.00,0:18:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,信号变弱了, 已经要从雷达上消失了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}It's fading, dropping out of our radar.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.88,0:18:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Jean, 给我接皇家空军, 那家飞机坠毁了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Jean, get me RAF Manston. That plane's crashed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.75,0:18:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,看变色龙的飞机! 肯定也出什么事了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Look at the Chameleon plane!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}There's something wrong with that too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.18,0:18:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,唔\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Hmmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.88,0:18:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,它停止不动了! 不可能啊\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}It's standing still! Impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.76,0:18:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,不, 先生, 光点是静止的\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}No sir, the blip's stationary.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.55,0:18:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,这只意味着一件事情\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}That can only mean one thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.81,0:18:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,它也坠毁了!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}It's crashing too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.01,0:19:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,立即向飞行甲板汇报\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Report to the flight deck immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.16,0:19:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,下一航班有多少人需要护照才能离开机场?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}How many people require passports\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}in order to leave the airport on the next flight?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.19,0:19:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,- 25个  - 这里你漏了一个\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Twenty-Five.  - You missed this one here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.26,0:19:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.92,0:19:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,继续吧\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Carry on.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.79,0:19:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,海上救援队报告说没有找到, 先生\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Negative report from Air Sea Rescue, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.35,0:19:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,但有两架飞机掉下去, 肯定会有残骸的痕迹啊\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}But with two aircraft ditching\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}there must be some signs of wreckage.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.77,0:19:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么觉得变色龙的飞机是坠落到海里了?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Why do you think the Chameleon plane\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}crashed into the sea?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.94,0:19:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,因为它从我们的雷达屏幕上消失了!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Because it disappeared off our radar screen!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.37,0:19:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,但它一开始是静止没动!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}But it stood still first!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.67,0:20:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,因为它肯定是跟空军的飞机撞上了, 然后掉落下去\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Because it must have collided with\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}the RAF plane and dropped like a stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.87,0:20:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么会这么想\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Why do you think that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.61,0:20:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,要知道, 当一架飞机像那样在雷达上静止不动\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}You see, when a plane on that radar\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}appears to stand still,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.71,0:20:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,那么它事实上就是直线下落了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}it is in point of fact dropping straight down.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.40,0:20:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,- 直线上升怎么样?   - 噢, 我亲爱的博士\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- What about straight up?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Oh my dear Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.29,0:20:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,要能像那样跑出我们雷达的范围\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}To get above our radar umbrella like that
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.77,0:20:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,它必须垂直爬上达到100英里高\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}it'd have to climb vertically\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}until it was a hundred miles high.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.92,0:20:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,那该死的高度就是外太空了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}The darned thing would be in outer space.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.46,0:20:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,正是这个!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Exactly!
